{"tid":467481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iPhone X OLED 屏幕再傳災情，無故現發長綠色的「死亡光線」","createTime":"2017-11-13T14:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T09:38:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e52eee4056d67cf28e01b176cb5d2cec3a027f6e","tid":467481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"iPhone X 自推出後，市場反應雖然十分理想，但隨著用戶開始使用後，很快便被發現出現各類疑似是品質上的問題。其中最嚴重的問題，就是首次採用 Samsung 的 OLED 屏幕，最近不少用戶回報左側或右側有機會出現<span style=\"color: red;\">一條長長的綠色「死亡線」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/iPhone-X-green-line1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FiPhone-X-green-line1.png&h=cd782447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫時未知 Apple 何時能夠解決這問題</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/11/12/iphone-x-oled-screen-green-line/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2Fiphone-x-oled-screen-green-line%2F&d=XXEMUvUsQU%2Fwn%2BSu3dOWCf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5ac01e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/11/12/iphone-x-oled-screen-green-line/</a>"},{"pid":"223ea7cb309ae31da03887b4153d730c5d62cc7c","tid":467481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5d8c189f0da1f0a29adafa4d30624ba53bdc4d","tid":467481,"uid":66686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"軟件問題？"},{"pid":"2965e5efa046d16072f219064ad0349981daedf1","tid":467481,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img s